    <p>Full benchmark results are shown in <xref rid="sup1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Supplementary Tables S1</xref> and <xref rid="sup1" ref-type="supplementary-material">S2</xref>, summarised in <xref rid="btad728-T1" ref-type="table">Table 1</xref>, and described here. <xref rid="btad728-T1" ref-type="table">Table 1</xref> includes results for Hostile run with a masked database. <xref rid="sup1" ref-type="supplementary-material">Supplementary Table S3</xref> includes accession numbers for all datasets used. Refer to the Supplementary Text for detailed information about test data preparation.</p>
